Events.RelatedBody:
catalog2dnx should extract the packaged icon file to the flat container.
If package does not contain packaged icon but contains package URL, the following happens:
* It will attempt to retrieve the URL content;
  * If content length is longer than size limit, ignore the content and don't emit `iconUrl`;
* It will check if the retrieved content is an image of the supported format;
  * if it is not a supported image, ignore the content and don't emit `iconUrl`;
* If all is fine, saves the icon into the flat container.
